comment._content:
Prototype Douglas XA-3D-1 Skywarrior Bu No 125412 
Powered by unsuccessful Westinghouse XJ40 engines.
Overall midnight blue scheme. Douglas logo aft of cockpit.
First cockpit framing design, fairing for periscope beneath forward fuselage. 
Representative shapes for rear radar and gun turret.
Bullet fairing on tip of vertical tail.
